values: WHOOT!! my Birthday today!! Updates later!!
ever get sick of being used? I do.

Got an SOS from an old friend today, so went and entertained her for a while and then went out into the clubs last nite to amuse her and enjoy the 'nightlife' (I use that description somewhat liberally -- I don't know that having 2 brain cells quite meets the necssary prerequisites for 'life') .

hhmmmm should say more .. but that will have to wait until morning;
